data.description: This gem is the perfect starter home or looking to downsize. Remodeled kitchen and fresh paint. Three bedrooms with primary apart from other two bedrooms. Large soaking tub and large walk in closet in the primary. Additional bedrooms are great size for kids or guest. Dining and kitchen combo is great for entertaining. Granite countertops and new back splash make the kitchen very inviting. Newer roof in the last 2 years, new siding north side, and new front gate. Huge deck in back yard is the perfect hangout spot! This home has charm and is ready for its new owners!!! BOOK YOUR SHOWING TODAY!!!
